snippet.title: Ugetsu Kitan / 雨月奇譚 (Longplay 1/5)
snippet.description:
This is a longplay of Ugetsu Kitan, a Visual Novel game published by Tonkin House and developed by Will for the Playstation 1. It was released in 1996. It is a remake of the PC98 game that was released in 1992. Ugetsu Kitan is based on Ugetsu Monogatari, a collection of nine supernatural tales by the Japanese author Ueda Akinari.

Longplay note: I cannot read or speak Japanese, so this playthrough may seem like a speed-run. 

More info about the game at:

http://www.vidyasaur.com/2016/10/ugetsu-kitan.html
